      "raw_text": "Federal union No. 1922 Is now\none of, II not the largest federal\nunion In the country. The union\nnumbers nearly 900 men, and is In\ncreasing its membership every\nmeeting. Recently the laborers\nemployed on the Inland Empire\nlines were added to the rolls.\n\n\nAmong other recruits gathered in\nby the big federal last night was\nJames J. Daley. weather prophet,\npolitical forecaster and philosopher.\nMr.. Daley Is New Zealander,\nwhere all the people are unionists,\nand he cannot keep out of some la\nDor organization, so he cast his\nlot with the local federal. He is\ndeputy in the Office of the city\ncomptroller."
